sourcesContent: import { IonContent, IonHeader, IonIcon, IonItem, IonLabel, IonList, IonMenu, IonMenuToggle, IonTitle, IonToolbar, IonAvatar, IonButton } from '@ionic/react'; import React from 'react'; import { RouteComponentProps, withRouter } from 'react-router-dom'; import { AppPage } from '../declarations'; interface MenuProps extends RouteComponentProps { appPages: AppPage[]; } const Menu: React.FunctionComponent = ({ appPages }) => ( Shady Alzayat {appPages.map((appPage, index) => { return ( {appPage.title} ); })} window.open('https://www.linkedin.com/in/shadyalzayat/', '_system') } > Resources Ionic Documentation Scaffold Out Your App Change Your App Layout Theme Your App ); export default withRouter(Menu);
